Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:04.00,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\fad(500,500)}翻译：绿豆  小怡       时间：恩底米昂之鹰       压制：Tanaous     后期：Salty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私设武装组织天行者以根除战争为名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始武力介入世界范围内产生的纷争已经过了5年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着这因为天行者的武力介入而满目疮痍的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 这重生…是否能说是正确的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世间的扭曲 如今还栗然再目不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使们的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.70,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}公元2301年 库鲁吉斯共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争是献给神的圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24世纪初 世界从化石燃料时代转变为太阳光发电时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:27.08,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}蔑视神圣 争夺神之土地的无神论者们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.72,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我们将降下制裁的铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场改革的战争中 幼小的我被卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这生与死的交错之处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那台机体相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和命运的机体 Gundam相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2307年 我们私设武装组织天行者开始了行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,240082 Exia 目标地点确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散布 在到达目标地点后终止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标对象确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定 开始第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 竟然还有一台新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些光点…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2个世纪前死掉的天才宇宙物理学家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·肖汉博格所提言的世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙… 还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在模拟战中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两千次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不败的战绩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 第一阶段完成 开始第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为之而生的4台机体 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 目标瞄准狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 轰炸目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然变形了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 捕获目标 日掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 光束剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.88,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ビームサーベル（Beem Saber）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要根绝战争之类的觉悟 让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你得手么!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续的对各个纷争区域的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,促成了我和某个男人命运的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及和某个人命运的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作被看透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈 机体不错但驾驶员看来还嫩点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? Gundam先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个劲只会打扰我做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和过去我所属的游击队KPSA的头目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就收下了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞并了我的故国库鲁吉斯共和国的阿扎帝斯坦王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其年轻的王女相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两庄际遇 逐渐交集到阿扎帝斯坦王国的内乱中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向忘记神的教导的人们给与神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱赶走那些进入契约之地的异教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生战争就会有人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果纷争继续的话 总有一天我会去阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的事情 把这个国家引向了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 我品尝到了无尽的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 当不了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 有机影正在接近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UNION的侦查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那台白色的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 知道政变的主谋是沙歇斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就决定了再次战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要 为了成为Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 那时候的小屁孩居然坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战斗还没有结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁吉斯都毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的神在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没义务回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了 这机体还是让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这小子摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按计划进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下 天行者组织发来了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者组织发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马苏德·拉夫玛迪被保护 正向王宫行进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后 我慢慢的首次发现作为Gundam战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放正保护的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放正保护的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是否还会前来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你所相信的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.86,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UNION 大总统府
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.70,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}人革连 国家主席室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.91,*Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AEU中央议会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从世上根除战争而创立的武装组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是即由天行者的武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得世界能够统一成一体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拥有压倒性武装能力的Gundam为手段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将纷争逐一击破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一击 结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 开始装填
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这数量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为了对抗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是伊奥利亚计划的一部分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了世界的统一而存在的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我们的只有毁灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所不知的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崔尼蒂小队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也自称是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们所进行的武力介入和我们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对各个军事基地的无差别攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向一般市民攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸… 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸! 妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易买下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没办法戴上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam的所为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驱除目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不配做Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 万死难辞其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是三对三了 要公平竞赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们相比 你有应该先解决的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是 尼尔·狄兰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔·狄兰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那场战斗中 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我过去所属的游击队KPSA发起的自杀性恐怖袭击 而失去亲人的洛克昂的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 此刻我几乎无法抑制干掉你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给我的家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的怨念得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我干掉你就不能如愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我校正这畸形的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我还活着 我就会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非作为索兰·依伯拉罕而是作为天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶着Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太傻瓜了 我都射不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个了不得的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的称赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荚舱 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我们的战斗迎来了最终的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载了GN drive的联合国军的猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么只是擦到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有压倒性优势的Gundam的性能 如今也丧失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们的灭亡也是计划里的一步么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 和夺走Throne Zwei的亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯的再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的男人不配驾驶Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不需要你来许可!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这可就玩完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 那动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放了 TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 拉塞所说的话在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我认为天行者组织 我们的存在不是有意义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场战斗中 洛克昂和家族的仇人对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这制造战争的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使Dynames被破坏了 那个男人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的 躲哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们满意了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能满意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消除纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是除了战斗一无所知的破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒眼前的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要纠正这扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即由武力的根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这才是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam所应有的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我 我们是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这4年里 我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注目着我们天行者 Gundam所引发的世界变革
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 这重生…是否能说是正确的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世间的扭曲 如今还栗然再目不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还存在着扭曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新的机体 00 Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士Gundam 00 第二季
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度降临的天使们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开新的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2312年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了地球联邦政府的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创建了独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了以地球统一为名的镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了纠正这个扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者再次站了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新番组 机动战士Gundam 00
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10月5日 周日下午5点 武力介入开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那重生毁灭


